quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  14,13,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi ezithunyweni zabo, “ngempela sizonigxosha ezweni lethu noma nibuyele enkolweni yethu ngakho-ke iNkosi yabo yembula (isambulo) kubona (yathi), “ngempela sizozibhubhisa izoni”"
  14,14,"Futhi ngempela sizonizinzisa emhlabeni emva kwabo, lokhu okwalowo owesaba ukuma phambi kwami futhi owesaba ukusonga kwami"
  14,15,"Futhi babefuna ukunqoba nosizo, futhi bonke ababephika (ubunye bukaMvelinqangi) baholelwa ekudukeni nasekubhujisweni"
  14,16,Isihogo siyoba singaphambi kwakhe futhi uyophuziswa amanzi abilayo aphuma ezilondeni zabantu basesihogweni
  14,17,Uyowaphuza engathandi futhi ethola ubunzima ekuwagwinyeni bese ukufa kuyeza kuyena zinhlangothi zonke kepha angafi futhi ngaphambili kwakhe kuyobe kunesijeziso esinzima kakhulu
  14,18,"Isibonelo salabo abangakholwanga eNkosini yabo ukuthi imisebenzi yabo injengemilotha ephephethwa isivunguvungu somoya ngosuku lwezivunguvungu, abanamandla ngalutho kulokho ababekusebenzela, lokho kungukuduka okukude le"
  14,19,Ngakube awuboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso na? Uma ethanda anganisusa (anganibhubhisa) bese eletha indalo entsha
  14,20,Futhi lokho kuMvelinqangi akunzima nakancane (ukuthi akwenze)
  14,21,"Futhi bonke bayovela kuMvelinqangi labo ababuthakathaka bayothi kulabo ababeqhosha “ngempela thina sasingabalandeli benu, ngakubeni nina ningasisiza ngokuthize esijezisweni sikaMvelinqangi na? Bayothi, “ukube uMvelinqangi wayesiholile sasizonihola, kuyefana kuthina noma ngabe asibekezeli noma siyabekezela angeke sikwazi ukuphunyuka”"